        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2018-10-10 00:13:30.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Now that LUTF is being worked upon to be build along with lustre. I\n > am thinking, I will push a patch under the same ticket to add the\n > test-script to LUTF which test this functionality.\n > Since LUTF is on multi-rail branch, so that patch will go to\n > multi-rail branch.\n\nThat is fine, as long as it is something that is tested with every patch, and is something easily run by developers.  I've been hearing about LUTF for a long time, but haven't seen it yet.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
